# ─── Excalibur Forensic Migration Agent ───
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN is required for:
#   1. GitHub Models API (LLM) — included with Copilot subscription
#   2. Repository PR sync (optional) — reading PR diffs
#
# How to get it:
#   Option A: gh auth token  (if you have GitHub CLI)
#   Option B: Create a PAT at https://github.com/settings/tokens
#
# In PowerShell:
#   $env:GITHUB_TOKEN = (gh auth token)

GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
